    [ctns_front]
Addition Property of Zero (0)
    [/ctns_front]

    [ctns_back]
For all real numbers $$x \in \mathbb{R},$$
$| x+0 = x. |$
    [/ctns_back]

    [ctns_frontspeak]
Addition Property of Zero
    [/ctns_frontspeak]

    [ctns_backspeak]
For all real numbers X, -- the sum of X plus zero equals X.
    [/ctns_backspeak]

